name: QuestNG
overview:
What is Questng? Questng was formerly called Onenigeriasearch. Questng is a search engine that is dedicated to enabling businesspeople and other visitors find results of business related searches. Questng provides answers to quests from within and outside Nigeria.

Questng provides information relating to Nigeria by indexing very informative and high quality sites in Nigeria. These sites are reindexed frequently to provide you with current information at all times. We index site that only contain contents that are;

Economical Political Informative Educational Technological Traditional Business Oriented Social etc. Thus providing quality results to your quests.

Questng also manages a web-based business catalogue that serves many types of organizations; Companies Schools Hotels Guest houses Restaurants Hospitals Shops/Malls
